title: GATE 2024 Admit Card Released
content: GATE 2024 admit cards are now available for download. Candidates can access their admit cards from the official GATE website using their login credentials.

title: JEE Main 2024 Registration Extended
content: The registration deadline for JEE Main 2024 has been extended to December 15, 2023. Students can now register through the official NTA website.
